mixin Disclaimer-modal()
    div(id="modal" class="modal")
      div(class="modal-content")
        h2 Disclaimer
        p Participation in fantasy sports is governed by the laws applicable in India. Fantasy sports are classified as a 'game of skill' under Indian law and are legal in most states. 
        p However, residents of Andhra Pradesh, Assam, Nagaland, Odisha, Sikkim, and Telangana are not eligible to participate due to state-specific regulations. 
        p Users must be at least 18 years old to register and participate. 
        p Please ensure you play responsibly and comply with the applicable laws before engaging in any activities on this platform.
        button(id="confirm-btn") Confirm